skid/skids
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:usually pl. as THE SKIDS, a slip-way for storing and handling logs at a sawmill
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also bush skids
